{"tid":84969,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲高爾澄清並非退休","createTime":"2017-01-18T02:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T05:31:31.000Z","uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4e00edd8c5e32682585b5b220fc1a52f3e4433","tid":84969,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:51:47.000Z","msg":"雲高爾：係休息！唔係退休！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://sports.now.com/sport/news/4/014/17101130014/17105634857_600x408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F4%2F014%2F17101130014%2F17105634857_600x408.jpg&h=5c9ebe9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Kxubg5lyxominCtMoJIXmYscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=3da6a061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】玩咩！前曼聯領隊雲高爾澄清退休報道，堅稱自己正在休息而非退休，到7月才有決定。<br />\n<br />\n有戰術大師之稱的前曼聯領隊雲高爾（Louis van Gaal）創下轉軚紀錄，他日前接受荷蘭《電訊報》訪問表示自己無意再執教球隊，令各大媒體爭相報道他退休的消息。不過，他在周二晚接受西班牙《Cadena Ser》電台訪問，卻澄清退休的說法。<br />\n<br />\n「不，不，不，我沒有退休。我僅僅是休息而已，之後我會再決定是否退休。一切都視乎收到的條件而定，7月再定！」原來，今年夏天才是雲高爾的D-Day，還收到西甲球隊的邀約。<br />\n<br />\n「我可能重返西班牙。1個月或5周之前，華倫西亞邀請我擔任教練，當時我回絕了。」雲高爾說。該荷蘭名帥之前還拒絕過中超球隊的盛情，據悉3季酬勞高達4400萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp17101130014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp17101130014&d=Kxubg5lyxominCtMoJIXmYscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=7aad575d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp17101130014&h=6651a4cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp17101130014</a>"},{"pid":"243107a78780a229e876591f9eb2a2fce81efdd5","tid":84969,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T02:58:53.000Z","msg":"敢唔敢？"},{"pid":"54c54a5c41eab41ffa0c659c734fc2e16a46d4bb","tid":84969,"uid":46892,"like":0,"di